team_info.name: ahrar
team_info.description: Ahrar is a tech-savvy individual who enjoys indulging in his passions for cars, gadgets, and video games.

team_info.name: hamed
team_info.description: Hamed is a unique individual who loves to immerse himself in the world of video games, has a passion for collecting and playing retro consoles, and enjoys the simple pleasure of a rice and yogurt meal.

team_info.name: horam
team_info.description: Horam's interests are so intellectually demanding that his friends joke that spending time with him is like attending a lecture series on psychology, cognitive science, and design, all while listening to a symphony by Mozart - it's enough to make their heads spin. But at least they know who to turn to when they need help analyzing their dreams.

team_info.name: osama
team_info.description: Osama is a curious character with a quirky combination of interests - he loves to curl up with a good book, spend his free time swimming in the pool, and can't resist the charm of a fluffy feline. It's a combination that has his friends scratching their heads, but hey, who are we to judge?

team_info.name: ramin
team_info.description: Ramin is an avid gamer who spends most of his free time playing CSGO and also enjoys watching and playing football.

team_info.name: weng
team_info.description: Weng is a true multitasker who can often be found watching a movie while playing badminton and competing in a round of video games, all while somehow managing to keep his popcorn bowl intact.

team_info.name: zohreh
team_info.description: Zohreh is a creative and cultured individual who loves to cook up a storm in the kitchen, explore the world through travel, express herself through artwork, and get lost in the pages of a good book - it's a wonder she has time for anything else besides making her friends jealous with her Instagram posts.
